                    <div class="features__content-three">
                             <h2 class="title-1">Admissions</h2>
                             <p>Admission is a complex and lengthy process - this module manages the entire process from application-submission to admission-confirmation. The module can be user configured to a set of rules that then results in effortless application of criteria and policies on the compiled data, producing various reports that help the management in the admission process.</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 </div>
                 
