                         <div class="features__content-three">
                             <h2 class="title-13">Fee Management</h2>
                             <p>Fee collection comes with a host of choices viz. mode, period, device and gateway: parents can pay fees in-person or online via a choice of payment gateways, in monthly, term-wise or annual installments and from either a laptop or mobile. The fee collection has a live-feed into the dashboard.
</p>
