                         <div class="features__content-three">
                             <h2 class="title-7">Examinations</h2>
                             <p>Education boards such as CBSE, ICSE, SSLC, Matriculation are supported. Advanced functionality such as definition of the exam structure, factoring in working days, help in planning and the actual conduct of exams. <br>
Routine tasks such as exam timetable, hall-ticket, mark sheet, and report card generation are effortless.</p>
