                         <div class="features__content-three">
                             <h2 class="title-4">Management of Student & Staff</h2>
                             <p>Student portfolios are created, maintained and managed including Personal Information (PI), academic & cocurricular performance, student conduct (Remarks, promotion, leaving). The repository of such information speeds up later issuance of various certificates of transfer, bona fides, conduct, career path guidance and counselling etc.</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 </div>
                
