                         <div class="features__content-three">
                             <h2 class="title-5">Attendance - Student & Staff</h2>
                             <p>Biometrics and RFID-based attendance-gate utilities that have been integrated with the system, records attendance details such as late coming and absenteeism, leave application and sanction/permission that can be notified to the concerned, including parents. Parents can monitor attendance of their wards. Staff data is integrated with the payroll module.</p>
                         </div>
                     </div>
                 </div>
                 
