                             <h2 class="title-7">Homework</h2>
                             <p>Home-work Management module allows teachers to effortlessly assign, track, and evaluate home-work tasks. With an intuitive interface and automated multi modal notifications, students stay informed and organized, while parents can monitor their child’s progress.</p>
                         </div>
